      "text": "// Iterator chain\nlet sum: i32 = vec![1,2,3].iter()\n    .filter(|&&x| x > 1)\n    .map(|&x| x * 2)\n    .sum();\n\n// Lifetime annotation\nfn longest<'a>(x: &'a str, y: &'a str) -> &'a str\n\n// Closure with capture\nlet adder = |x: i32| x + captured_val;",
